                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-710-18630511 t18630511-710-punishment-55"></join>Confined Twelve Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">HOLDEN</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18630511-710-verdict-1" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18630511-710-verdict-1" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18630511-710-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.*</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Holden was further charged with having been before convicted of felony at Liverpool, on the</hi> 6<hi rend="italic">th April</hi>, 1860; <hi rend="italic">to which he</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">PLEADED GUILTY</hi>.—<hi rend="italic">
